********************************************************************************

What's next?

1. Add "include Clearance::App::Controllers::ApplicationController"
to your app/controllers/application.rb:

class ApplicationController < ActionController::Base
  include Clearance::App::Controllers::ApplicationController
...

2. If you had a User model already, add "include Clearance::App::Models::User"
to your app/models/user.rb:

class User < ActiveRecord::Base
  include Clearance::App::Models::User
...

3. Run "rake db:migrate"

********************************************************************************
